title: War of the Roses: The Old Guy on Zoom
description: Laura is starting to see a lot of red flags with her boyfriend Zane.  It started when she saw an extra key that he had.  Then a server said something very strange to them when they were out to eat that made Laura feel like Zane brings other girls there. And the list goes on.  So what is the explanation of all these red flags, cheating, or coincidence?
